Tripod_Nip: {
	Name: Tripod Nip
	Text:
		'''
		Post-Operation Log 448 ||
		<Name of Cubekon Tinkerer> Mares
							
		I figured it would’ve been obvious, the tripods are the most prominent predator in the wastelands. I’ve observed them behind the scenes, they always seem to go after my decoys first and make sure work that they were destroyed, and then immediately go after the substance. The drug has interesting effects on tripods that I haven’t seen in any other antibody; I found that the tripods would do one of the following actions when tripod nip was introduced: 1) rub their bodies all over it like some kind of cat, 2) dance excitedly, or 3) absorb it with some kind of appendage made of black bile and then make a run for it. I also went ahead to test the effects of the drug on rather unfortunate Defiled Cyclops [i:Origins/Defiled_Cyclops] and before it could even dispose of can, it was promptly absorbed by a tripod making a mad dash at it. It was a hilarious sight to see to the extent I broke out in laughter. Ever since that day, I’ve been too afraid to return to the wastes to do anymore testing. I'm sure if you had to chop of your leg from being side-swiped by a Defiled Tripod you were just laughing at, you'd be pretty traumatized too. And, <Name of Mechanic> really wonders why I set the darn place off limits... and specifically had to tell her not to feed the tripods no matter how adorable they are.
		'''
}

